Program: Outlook
Title: The Story of a Former Kidnap Victim in Sierra Leone
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbsbw
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
The Sierra Leone girl kidnapped by rebels now becoming a doctor thanks to an Italian woman. Also, 'Speak English' sign in Joey Vento's Philadelphia burger bar causes controversy. Update from Kyle MacDonald on his red-paperclip-for-a-house trades. Mathew Parris on the dangerous salt route camel trains in Ethiopia. Finally the scrap metal providing a source of income in Guinea-Bissau. Show less